{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"62dfe918-c01e-4b06-a12f-a5f91a9dd657","content":"Here's a value converter and XAML wiring:\n\n**OrderStatusToColorConverter.cs**\n\n```csharp\nusing System.Globalization;\n\nnamespace YourApp.Converters;\n\npublic class OrderStatusToColorConverter : IValueConverter\n{\n    public object Convert(object value, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)\n    {\n        return (OrderStatus)value switch\n        {\n            OrderStatus.Pending   => Colors.Orange,\n            OrderStatus.Shipped   => Colors.Blue,\n            OrderStatus.Delivered => Colors.Green,\n            OrderStatus.Cancelled => Colors.Red,\n            _ => Colors.Gray\n        };\n    }\n\n    public object ConvertBack(object value, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)\n        => throw new NotSupportedException();\n}\n```\n\n**XAML usage (e.g., OrderPage.xaml)**\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:converters=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.Converters\">\n\n    <ContentPage.Resources>\n        <converters:OrderStatusToColorConverter x:Key=\"StatusToColor\" />\n    </ContentPage.Resources>\n\n    <Label Text=\"{Binding Status}\"\n           TextColor=\"{Binding Status, Converter={StaticResource StatusToColor}}\" />\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- Register the converter in `<Page.Resources>` (or `App.xaml` for app-wide use).\n- The `Binding` passes the enum value; the converter returns a `Color`.\n- `ConvertBack` isn't needed for one-way display, so it throws.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"17f76ef9-d935-4284-8c14-0c9aa524311a","outputTokens":429,"requestId":"5035:2131E5:1BD53B5:1ED2055:69FA8F75"},"id":"d664168f-7dcd-4af1-b45c-07251135ccd2","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:46:53.466Z","parentId":"9fddd090-16fd-4833-9ad7-c6c75e82a3bf"}
